# Music Royalty Stream DCF Valuation Model

An Excel-based discounted cash flow (DCF) model for valuing a music royalty catalog using streaming revenue, per-stream rates, decay assumptions, and terminal value analysis.

## Overview

This model estimates the implied value of a music catalog by projecting future royalty cash flows from digital streaming platforms and discounting them back to present value.

It is designed for:
- Music catalog valuation.
- Royalty income analysis.
- Investment underwriting.
- Sensitivity analysis on key valuation drivers.

